-----------------------------------------------------
ADVENTURE_Mates
-----------------------------------------------------
ADVENTURE_Mates is a multiagent-based traffic and environment
simulator. The software has been developing by ADVENTURE project.

-----------------------------------------------------
DOCUMENTATION
-----------------------------------------------------
The necessary information about program operation can be found
in the manual file in "doc" directory.

The manual will be installed into <install_dir>/doc/AdvMates
by "make install", see below.

-----------------------------------------------------
INSTALLATION
-----------------------------------------------------
The following commands should be executed, after extraction of 
the package tar file and moving to a top directory 
"AdvMates-<Version name>". 

  % cmake .
  % make
  % make install

The default install directory is $HOME/ADVENTURE. It can be changed
at the cmake command with the option  -DINSTALL_PREFIX=<install_dir>. 

For example, 

  % cmake -DINSTALL_PREFIX=/usr/local .

will install files into /usr/local at "make install".
